OL,3,CMen charged in sexual exploitation
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FEight men have been charged with over
OL,7,F30 offences in an investigation into
OL,8,Fgroup-based child sexual exploitation.
OL,10,FDetectives from Gwent Police carried
OL,11,Fout a targeted operation on 14 July to
OL,12,Farrest the men, which included
OL,13,Factivity in Newport, Swansea, London,
OL,14,FBirmingham, Lancashire, Edinburgh and
OL,15,Fthe Argyll and Bute area in Scotland.
OL,17,FThe investigation was part of
OL,18,FOperation Oak, which looked into
OL,19,Freports of sexual abuse made by women
OL,20,Fwho were children at the time of the
OL,21,Falleged offences between 1985 and 1996.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
