OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784182683
OL,3,CMen charged in sexual exploitation
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fhas authorised 34 charges to the eight
OL,8,Fmen, including 17 counts of rape.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Superintendent, Andrew
OL,11,FTuck said: "Operation Oak is a complex
OL,12,Fand long-running investigation into
OL,13,Fgroup-based child sexual exploitation
OL,14,Fin south Wales.
OL,16,F"Through our partnership with the CPS,
OL,17,Fwe have now reached this significant
OL,18,Fstage in which eight men have been
OL,19,Fcharged.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784182683
OL,3,CMen charged in sexual exploitation
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,F"At the heart of our investigation has
OL,7,Fbeen supporting victims. Together with
OL,8,Fspecialist agencies, we are continuing
OL,9,Fto provide support to them".
OL,11,FHe added: "I know investigations of
OL,12,Fthis nature are likely to cause
OL,13,Fconcern in our communities, but it's
OL,14,Fvital to the victims in this case and
OL,15,Fthe integrity of the investigation
OL,16,Fthat nothing in posted on social media
OL,17,Fwhich could impact the court
OL,18,Fproceedings.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
